{"tid":1502042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"827 香港與亞馬遜同在集會 （純商討 未有定案）","createTime":"2019-08-24T14:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T15:41:17.000Z","uid":144833,"like":15,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"79254e1f36cece1a9f2c3b71b3fb1ec31681ff36","tid":1502042,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:28:17.000Z","msg":"我明白大家呢刻除咗香港 都無咩心機理其他野<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但亞馬遜森林絕對同你我有關！</span></span><br />\n當香港人不斷叫外國Stand With Hong Kong嘅時候 我地都應該更關注其他地方嘅事 仲要呢件事對我地都有好大影響 我地都要 Stand With Amazon<br />\n就算比我地爭取到五大訴求 無咗地球個肺 我地下一代都好難有命享<br />\n而巴西政府就好似我地個政府咁 淨係識叫外國勢力同環保團體唔好理 <br />\n<br />\n所以認真 不如發起集會去巴西領事館？<br />\n暫時諗住係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">827 香港與亞馬遜同在夜晚集會</span> </span><br />\n好處係唔使等多個禮拜 又唔會同遊行撞期 同埋可以快啲比到聲援 <br />\n<br />\n有諗過另外兩個option係：<br />\n1. 831 民陣大遊行 以亞馬遜森林呢個為主 一黎可以向巴西施壓 二黎可以話比國際知 我地唔係自私撚 我地都對地球環保有責任心 但係就擔心比人感覺會偏離咗五大訴求 同埋要問返民陣想唔想<br />\n2. 91 禮拜日個遊行先講亞馬遜 但個反響未必會好似831咁大 因為人數未必有咁多<br />\n但呢兩日嘅問題都在於 過咗成個禮拜先講會太遲<br />\n<br />\n你地點睇 比啲意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9b53f5917fa33b6fe52e90b5b41415d116ff8b","tid":1502042,"uid":308966,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"可考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c3cc49fdcefe9bfe01f5e2e995eb1de0d2925e","tid":1502042,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fc06bdba6d01393895cff69f37186983e0c9641","tid":1502042,"uid":54904,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:41:12.000Z","msg":"嚴重失焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d29744995f325f953b95c903725d2eeb625cc7","tid":1502042,"uid":155902,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:42:15.000Z","msg":"香港單野同亞馬遜有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a11396f7e801d00f575815313c4b250a0b2647","tid":1502042,"uid":66260,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"失焦, 夾硬將反送中同亞馬遜拉上關係可能會令巴西人反感"},{"pid":"53c9e7cc7a37608adbc136063ffcfdebe0808910","tid":1502042,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1fc06bdba6d01393895cff69f37186983e0c9641","tid":1502042,"uid":54904,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:41:12.000Z","msg":"嚴重失焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"所以諗住單獨一晚搞 唔撞遊行<br />\n當香港人一直叫緊國際社會關注嘅時候 我地都應該關注返國際發生緊嘅事 仲要咁大鑊"},{"pid":"287236d38ce6286c36b972fa2c500ef2be049912","tid":1502042,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06a11396f7e801d00f575815313c4b250a0b2647","tid":1502042,"uid":66260,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"失焦, 夾硬將反送中同亞馬遜拉上關係可能會令巴西人反感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:44:43.000Z","msg":"咁唔掛上反送中 淨係為亞馬遜單一議題發聲點睇"},{"pid":"84c1f66d68da4359bff855b0a5de804b79beae28","tid":1502042,"uid":247482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"香港都未搞掂而且比人數緊5:0<br />\n仲要開多條巴西戰線<br />\n<br />\n你香港比人屠城滅族班巴西人都唔會望一眼，唔好咁左膠"},{"pid":"ba95143560f5eb91449a68e9aebe97c41264861f","tid":1502042,"uid":281822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:06:51.000Z","msg":"唔好膠化啦仆街<br />\n死咗盲咗嘅義士同你玩熱帶雨林啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/d