ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e70450efbdf0b6dd1234575eaeb757332a5c48","tid":1502042,"uid":144833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ba95143560f5eb91449a68e9aebe97c41264861f","tid":1502042,"uid":281822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:06:51.000Z","msg":"唔好膠化啦仆街<br />\n死咗盲咗嘅義士同你玩熱帶雨林啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:12:04.000Z","msg":"到底關注亞馬遜點解會係膠化？<br />\n你真係覺得個森林燒到咁 唔會影響到我地？<br />\n依家唔係叫人唔再為義士爭取 <br />\n只係想分一日或者一晚嘅時間去表態<br />\n唔係香港發生嘅事就以事不關己嘅態度不聞不問<br />\n一黎就以膠化標籤<br />\n到時其他國家嘅人唔想理香港 真係唔好問點解"},{"pid":"491b411c0fcc0d499dcf944cba903734ed392c9f","tid":1502042,"uid":24009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:16:46.000Z","msg":"贊成<br />\n我地叫外國關注我地，我們都應該比返d關注人"},{"pid":"67d85809b9b92a64e2dc258948770036f6ebfe59","tid":1502042,"uid":144833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d62cbc20367cf60e8578fd4b01924fcaecfb9d06","tid":1502042,"uid":74155,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:09:57.000Z","msg":"呢啲已經唔係和理非<br />\n係堅左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets